WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:03.230
I was told that you were dead.

00:03.360 --> 00:04.589
But he did not...

00:04.720 --> 00:06.711
Yes, but I was told this.

00:06.840 --> 00:09.798
I will talk to her. My word on it.

00:09.920 --> 00:11.319
I do not see an animal, Nathaniel.

00:11.440 --> 00:15.354
NATHANIEL: And what if we left this
place? Robin as well.

00:15.480 --> 00:18.518
Robin Sumner,
you trust me, don't you?

00:19.840 --> 00:21.353
I'll see you safe.

00:21.480 --> 00:24.711
You've been a very brave boy, Robin.

00:28.960 --> 00:30.553
JACKSON: Well, that boy's dead,

00:30.680 --> 00:32.830
washed up like garbage
in the mud of Goodluck Hope.

00:32.960 --> 00:35.998
It's your piece-of-shit brother,
killing on account of your killing,

00:36.120 --> 00:37.599
you goddamn animals.

00:39.680 --> 00:41.910
DRUMMOND: There is a candle, sir.

00:46.680 --> 00:48.159
(BONE CRUNCHES)

00:51.960 --> 00:52.995
No!

00:53.120 --> 00:56.112
Mathilda! We had to catch him!

00:58.000 --> 01:04.074
